{"tid":685054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陣間會有班廢老黎見工 想下個馬威","createTime":"2018-05-31T06:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T07:21:44.000Z","uid":28007,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6809a2fde3c3fbf92c5566fe54eb494074ef0fb7","tid":685054,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:07:29.000Z","msg":"咁就茶記仔諗住請人 <br />\n老細話比個機會我去做hr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁依家完左晏市 啲廢老開始黎見工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生第一次 當然好緊張<br />\n柒左就一世<br />\n想一黎就下番個馬威比班廢老睇睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比佢地知道入左黎做都唔好諗住睇少我<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49eaf22b1d3d66ec682231049bde8324e6f5c6f0","tid":685054,"uid":48066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"叫佢地係所有應徵者兩分鐘自我介紹"},{"pid":"237a4f0975159a354a0df42715bf11c4849ed65c","tid":685054,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"依家啲朋友都係叫我入廚房放把老牛係腰間<br />\nShow番個勢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d366e74d4d00a8dd5d4cbc25cd83af0c45efd02a","tid":685054,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49eaf22b1d3d66ec682231049bde8324e6f5c6f0","tid":685054,"uid":48066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"叫佢地係所有應徵者兩分鐘自我介紹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"保障私隱 要逐個逐個in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ea0e5ac780a9bdb9915f6bd2f9161a9efd7c25","tid":685054,"uid":48066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"用英文落單"},{"pid":"fba35f9024d7d6e54888b7e63142266ded6d1111","tid":685054,"uid":76098,"like":2,"d